metadata.name: retrospective 001
metadata.description:
"retrospective" is a collection of NFT art blocks that blends the nostalgia of retro vintage aesthetics with the innovation of modern contemporary art.

Each art block is a unique piece that combines elements of vintage abstract vector art with a contemporary, cutting-edge feel.

The collection as a whole is a retrospective look at the evolution of art and the role that technology has played in shaping it, inviting viewers to contemplate the connection between past & present.
